glosses: To care, to consider important or valuable, to place importance on, to set store by, to value.

examples.text: Babası, yaşamı boyunca onun tahsiline çok ehemmiyet verdi.
examples.translation: Her father placed great importance on her education all his life.

etymology: Compound of ehemmiyet (“importance”) + vermek (“to give”), literally “to give importance”.
